# Vendored r2-wasm bundle — produced by `wasm-pack build` upstream,
# committed here so GitHub Pages can serve the static webapp without
# a Rust toolchain in CI. Ignore the developer-only build noise but
# track the runtime files the page actually imports.
*
!r2_wasm.js
!r2_wasm_bg.wasm
!r2_wasm.d.ts
!r2_wasm_bg.wasm.d.ts
!package.json
!.gitignore
